{"type":"message","id":"1581c4ec","parentId":"0c789fde","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:43:50.066Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md file and follow its instructions strictly.\n\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 6:42 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nLet me read the HEARTBEAT.md file to understand what periodic tasks need attention.","thinkingSignature":"f28f476d7239241b754728092902c496f3f7a74817832cca024f378d437fb1b7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ui710zjez6ie_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":99,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":38561,"totalTokens":38785,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774176225418}}
{"type":"message","id":"384127a3","parentId":"1581c4ec","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:43:50.290Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ui710zjez6ie_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774176230281}}
{"type":"message","id":"d3b22102","parentId":"384127a3","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:43:57.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Current time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 6:42 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nToday is a Sunday, which is a non-trading day. Let me check:\n\n1. **Workspace backup** - I should check if there's a checklist for this and if it needs to run.\n2. **Quant ops** - Today is Sunday, non-trading day, so no盘前强检 needed. But daily audit / 实盘面板 might still run if configured for non-trading days. Let me check the quant ops checklist.\n3. **Self-improvement** - I should check the self-improvement checklist.\n\nAlso need to check Active Task Monitoring - check if there's an ACTIVE_TASK.md with Status=active.\n\n\nI'll need to examine all three checklists to understand what the current operational status is.","thinkingSignature":"4d45ba73801e2fd18d6a26199d0910824c74922000ca729eeb3cf83f31ac9b8a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_orgnzqc23eyg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ 2>/dev/null && cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md 2>/dev/null; cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md 2>/dev/null; cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md 2>/dev/null; cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":943,"output":305,"cacheRead":38440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774176230293}}
{"type":"message","id":"08547570","parentId":"d3b22102","timestamp":"2026-03-22T10:43:57.487Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_orgnzqc23eyg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ACTIVE_TASK.md\nACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY\nACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md\n_tmp\nheartbeat-quant-ops.md\nheartbeat-self-improvement.md\nheartbeat-workspace-backup.md\nhighest_priority_execution_queue_20260319.md\nworkspace-maintenance.md\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n# 投研系统优化任务\n\n## 目标\n优化投研组量化系统，使其每天自动生成可执行、稳定的晨报\n\n## 验收标准\n1. 明天（2026-03-23）08:00 晨报准时发出\n2. 晨报内容：市场宽度、系统审计、持仓概览、BUY/SELL信号、风控红线\n3. 非交易日（周日）管道不崩溃\n\n## 任务清单\n\n### P0（管道不崩溃）\n- [x] 1. 修复 chief_broadcast.py 的 JSON 解析错误 → **已确认无问题**：Mar 21 20:42 夜间broadcast成功生成，dashboard JSON全部合法\n- [x] 2. 修复 data_source_health_probe 失败问题 → **需验证**：等待mlruns grep完成\n- [x] 3. 修复 event_watch 和 temporary_meeting 失败问题 → **需验证**\n- [x] 4. ✅ **已修复**：`run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh` 中 `REPORT_DIR` 未export导致 unbound variable 错误（Mar 19管道失败原因）\n- [x] 5. `halt_new_buy=true` 从周五（Mar 20）延续 → **预期行为**：市场下跌3.6%触发风控保护，非bug；周一盘前会重新计算\n\n### P1（内容质量）\n- [ ] 6. 验证晨报包含真实市场宽度数据\n- [ ] 7. 验证持仓概览显示真实持仓（25只A股）\n- [ ] 8. 验证 BUY/SELL 信号显示\n- [ ] 9. 验证风控红线显示\n\n### P2（可执行性）\n- [ ] 10. 晨报加入具体个股的目标价/止损价\n- [ ] 11. 晨报加入持仓盈亏分析（如能获取实时行情）\n\n### P3（稳定性）\n- [ ] 12. 所有 LaunchAgent cron job 注册验证\n- [ ] 13. 测试周日管道完整运行\n- [ ] 14. 生成完整工作报告\n\n## 当前状态\n- P0: REPORT_DIR已修复；chief_broadcast无JSON问题；halt_new_buy为预期风控行为\n- P1-P3: 待处理\n- 周一（Mar 23）盘前需验证08:50晨报是否正常发出\n\n## 执行记录\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: REPORT_DIR export缺失修复（run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh）\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: 确认 chief_broadcast JSON解析正常（Mar 21 20:42成功）\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: 确认 halt_new_buy=true 为预期行为（Mar 20市场下跌-3.629%触发风控）"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":35,"aggregated":"ACTIVE_TASK.md\nACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY\nACTIVE_TASK_TEMPLATE.md\n_tmp\nheartbeat-quant-ops.md\nheartbeat-self-improvement.md\nheartbeat-workspace-backup.md\nhighest_priority_execution_queue_20260319.md\nworkspace-maintenance.md\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n# 投研系统优化任务\n\n## 目标\n优化投研组量化系统，使其每天自动生成可执行、稳定的晨报\n\n## 验收标准\n1. 明天（2026-03-23）08:00 晨报准时发出\n2. 晨报内容：市场宽度、系统审计、持仓概览、BUY/SELL信号、风控红线\n3. 非交易日（周日）管道不崩溃\n\n## 任务清单\n\n### P0（管道不崩溃）\n- [x] 1. 修复 chief_broadcast.py 的 JSON 解析错误 → **已确认无问题**：Mar 21 20:42 夜间broadcast成功生成，dashboard JSON全部合法\n- [x] 2. 修复 data_source_health_probe 失败问题 → **需验证**：等待mlruns grep完成\n- [x] 3. 修复 event_watch 和 temporary_meeting 失败问题 → **需验证**\n- [x] 4. ✅ **已修复**：`run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh` 中 `REPORT_DIR` 未export导致 unbound variable 错误（Mar 19管道失败原因）\n- [x] 5. `halt_new_buy=true` 从周五（Mar 20）延续 → **预期行为**：市场下跌3.6%触发风控保护，非bug；周一盘前会重新计算\n\n### P1（内容质量）\n- [ ] 6. 验证晨报包含真实市场宽度数据\n- [ ] 7. 验证持仓概览显示真实持仓（25只A股）\n- [ ] 8. 验证 BUY/SELL 信号显示\n- [ ] 9. 验证风控红线显示\n\n### P2（可执行性）\n- [ ] 10. 晨报加入具体个股的目标价/止损价\n- [ ] 11. 晨报加入持仓盈亏分析（如能获取实时行情）\n\n### P3（稳定性）\n- [ ] 12. 所有 LaunchAgent cron job 注册验证\n- [ ] 13. 测试周日管道完整运行\n- [ ] 14. 生成完整工作报告\n\n## 当前状态\n- P0: REPORT_DIR已修复；chief_broadcast无JSON问题；halt_new_buy为预期风控行为\n- P1-P3: 待处理\n- 周一（Mar 23）盘前需验证08:50晨报是否正常发出\n\n## 执行记录\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: REPORT_DIR export缺失修复（run_paper_trading_profiles_auto_v1.sh）\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: 确认 chief_broadcast JSON解析正常（Mar 21 20:42成功）\n- 2026-03-22 05:44: 确认 halt_new_buy=true 为预期行为（Mar 20市场下跌-3.629%触发风控）","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774176237483}}
